Title: Pegler VSH Tectite TS3 male iron straight connector 15mm x 1/2"
Description: This VSH Tectite 316 TS3/TS243G 15mm x 1/2" connector includes push-fit x BSP tapered male thread end connections. Tectite 316 is a stainless steel option developed specifically for use with the 316 System tube for potable water applications where water quality and hygiene are of utmost importance. The Tectite 316 range includes a stainless steel grab ring designed to grip a stainless steel tube with no need for scribing.
